# 🎯 12. Common Mistakes ❌

## ❌ Wrong month

```js
new Date(2026, 3, 25) // April, not March
```

---

## ❌ String parsing issues

```js
new Date("03-25-2026") // unreliable ⚠️
```

✔ Use:

```js
new Date("2026-03-25")
```

